{"hash":"468f19afe8ff15e458af04a6d71f8a5f519729c1","data":{"markdownPage":{"id":"9022e57aa136a6b493f9137f114cd3c8","title":"Process-GPT 安装指南","description":"","path":"/zh/getting-started/process-gpt-install/","timeToRead":1,"content":"<h1 id=\"process-gpt-安装指南\"><a href=\"#process-gpt-%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E6%8C%87%E5%8D%97\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Process-GPT 安装指南</h1>\n<p>本指南将帮助您快速安装和配置 Process-GPT。</p>\n<h2 id=\"系统要求\"><a href=\"#%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>系统要求</h2>\n<p>在开始安装之前，请确保您的系统满足以下要求：</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>操作系统</strong>: Windows 10+, macOS 10.15+, 或 Linux</li>\n<li><strong>内存</strong>: 最少 4GB RAM (推荐 8GB+)</li>\n<li><strong>存储</strong>: 至少 2GB 可用空间</li>\n<li><strong>网络</strong>: 稳定的互联网连接</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"安装步骤\"><a href=\"#%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E6%AD%A5%E9%AA%A4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>安装步骤</h2>\n<h3 id=\"1-下载安装包\"><a href=\"#1-%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BD%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E5%8C%85\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>1. 下载安装包</h3>\n<p>从官方网站下载最新版本的 Process-GPT：</p>\n<pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token comment\"># 使用 npm 安装</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">npm</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-g</span> process-gpt\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># 或使用 yarn 安装  </span>\n<span class=\"token function\">yarn</span> global <span class=\"token function\">add</span> process-gpt</code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"2-验证安装\"><a href=\"#2-%E9%AA%8C%E8%AF%81%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>2. 验证安装</h3>\n<p>安装完成后，验证安装是否成功：</p>\n<pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">process-gpt <span class=\"token parameter variable\">--version</span></code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"3-初始化配置\"><a href=\"#3-%E5%88%9D%E5%A7%8B%E5%8C%96%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>3. 初始化配置</h3>\n<p>运行初始化命令设置您的工作环境：</p>\n<pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">process-gpt init</code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"下一步\"><a href=\"#%E4%B8%8B%E4%B8%80%E6%AD%A5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>下一步</h2>\n<p>安装完成后，您可以：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>📖 阅读<a href=\"../advanced-features/user-guide/\">用户指南</a></li>\n<li>🎯 查看<a href=\"../tutorial/tutorial-lv1/\">教程</a></li>\n<li>💬 体验 <a href=\"../advanced-features/ai-chat-guide/\">AI 聊天功能</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"需要帮助\"><a href=\"#%E9%9C%80%E8%A6%81%E5%B8%AE%E5%8A%A9\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>需要帮助？</h2>\n<p>如果您在安装过程中遇到问题，请：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>查看<a href=\"../advanced-features/user-guide/\">常见问题</a></li>\n<li>联系技术支持</li>\n<li>访问社区论坛</li>\n</ul>\n<p>祝您使用愉快！🎉</p>\n","sidebar":"getting-started","headings":[{"depth":1,"value":"Process-GPT 安装指南","anchor":"#process-gpt-安装指南"},{"depth":2,"value":"系统要求","anchor":"#系统要求"},{"depth":2,"value":"安装步骤","anchor":"#安装步骤"},{"depth":3,"value":"1. 下载安装包","anchor":"#1-下载安装包"},{"depth":3,"value":"2. 验证安装","anchor":"#2-验证安装"},{"depth":3,"value":"3. 初始化配置","anchor":"#3-初始化配置"},{"depth":2,"value":"下一步","anchor":"#下一步"},{"depth":2,"value":"需要帮助？","anchor":"#需要帮助"}]},"allMarkdownPage":{"edges":[{"node":{"path":"/ko/getting-started/process-gpt-install/","title":"로컬 설치 가이드"}},{"node":{"path":"/ko/getting-started/","title":"Process-GPT 소개"}},{"node":{"path":"/ko/tutorial/tutorial-lv5/","title":"멀티플 인스턴스로 실행하는 고객 맞춤 뉴스레터 프로세스"}},{"node":{"path":"/ko/tutorial/tutorial-lv4/","title":"ERP 데이터 연동을 통한 재고 관리"}},{"node":{"path":"/ko/tutorial/tutorial-lv2/","title":"AI 에이전트를 활용한 제안서 작성"}},{"node":{"path":"/ko/design-pattern/parallelization/","title":"3. Parallelization"}},{"node":{"path":"/ko/design-pattern/tool-use/","title":"4. Tool Use"}},{"node":{"path":"/ko/tutorial/tutorial-lv1/","title":"프로세스 생성과 실행"}},{"node":{"path":"/ko/design-pattern/routing/","title":"2. Routing (지능적 라